No chance. Not from that distance.

371
00:25:09,716 --> 00:25:11,592
打赌?庞博...
Wanna bet? Bombur...

372
00:25:11,843 --> 00:25:12,510
接着!
catch!

373
00:25:16,097 --> 00:25:17,014
我来帮你
I'll help you with that.

374
00:25:24,773 --> 00:25:25,564
哦 你这...
Oh, you great...

375
00:25:25,815 --> 00:25:26,857
大饭桶
galumphing git!

376
00:25:27,108 --> 00:25:28,150
谁还要麦芽酒? 给你
Who wants an ale? There you go.

377
00:25:28,401 --> 00:25:29,068
伙计 这里
Over here, brother.

378
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:31,320
你得再喝一杯...
I said have another drink...

379
00:25:31,571 --> 00:25:33,531
给你
Here you go.

380
00:25:38,662 --> 00:25:39,995
数三声干杯!
Ale on the count of three!

381
00:25:40,247 --> 00:25:40,913
一...
One...

382
00:25:41,164 --> 00:25:42,790
- 二...  - 干杯!
- two...  - Up!

383
00:25:54,052 --> 00:25:55,469
就知道你会这样!
I knew you had it in you!

384
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:58,264
抱歉 这是杯垫 不是抹布
Excuse me, that is a doily, not a dishcloth.

385
00:25:58,515 --> 00:25:59,557
都破成这样了
But it's full of holes.

386
00:25:59,808 --> 00:26:01,976
它就应该长这样 针织的
It's supposed to look like that. It's crochet.

387
00:26:02,227 --> 00:26:05,145
如果你喜欢的话 编织也是很好玩的
And a wonderful game it is too, if you've got the balls for it.

388
00:26:05,397 --> 00:26:07,231
这些矮人真讨厌!
Bebother and confusticate these Dwarves!

389
00:26:07,482 --> 00:26:10,150
亲爱的比尔博 你这是怎么了?
My dear Bilbo, what on earth is the matter?

390
00:26:10,402 --> 00:26:13,153
怎么了? 我家里一堆矮人
What's the matter? I'm surrounded by Dwarves.

391
00:26:13,405 --> 00:26:14,905
他们来这干什么?
What are they doing here?

392
00:26:15,156 --> 00:26:18,826
习惯了就会觉得他们是很欢乐的一群人了
Oh, they're quite a merry gathering once you get used to them.

393
00:26:19,077 --> 00:26:20,953
我不想习惯他们
I don't want to get used to them.

394
00:26:21,204 --> 00:26:24,290
瞧瞧我的厨房 地毯上踩的全是泥巴
Look at the state of my kitchen. There's mud trod into the carpet.

395
00:26:24,541 --> 00:26:25,874
储藏室也被一扫而光
They've pillaged the pantry.

396
00:26:26,126 --> 00:26:28,460
更别说他们在厕所干的事情了
I won't tell you what they've done in the bathroom.

397
00:26:28,712 --> 00:26:32,506
下水道都坏了 真不知道他们来我家干什么!
They've destroyed the plumbing. I don't understand what they're doing in my house!

398
00:26:32,757 --> 00:26:37,886
抱歉 打扰一下 这盘子该怎么处理?
Excuse me. I'm sorry to interrupt, but what should I do with my plate?

399
00:26:38,138 --> 00:26:40,347
这儿 欧力 给我吧
Here you go, Ori. Give it to me.

400
00:26:45,103 --> 00:26:45,769
放回来
Take that back.

401
00:26:46,021 --> 00:26:46,687
拜托
Excuse me.

402
00:26:47,147 --> 00:26:48,188
这是我母亲的...
That's my mother's...

403
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,940
西域陶瓷 已经有...
West Farthing pottery. It's over...

404
00:26:50,191 --> 00:26:51,358
100多年历史了!
100 years old!

405
00:26:54,821 --> 00:26:55,487
你们能...
And can you...

406
00:26:55,739 --> 00:26:56,488
不这样么?
not do that?

407
00:26:56,740 --> 00:26:57,406
刀子会变钝的
You'll blunt them.

408
00:26:57,657 --> 00:26:59,533
听他说啥了吗 小子们?
Ooh. Do you hear that, lads?

409
00:27:00,201 --> 00:27:00,993
他说...
He says...

410
00:27:01,244 --> 00:27:02,911
我们会把刀弄钝
we'll blunt the knives.

411
00:27:03,163 --> 00:27:04,997
# 刀子敲钝 叉子掰弯 #
# Blunt the knives, bend the forks #

412
00:27:05,248 --> 00:27:07,666
# 瓶子打破 木塞烧了 #
# Smash the bottles and burn the corks #

413
00:27:07,917 --> 00:27:09,668
# 杯子敲烂 盘子摔碎 #
# Chip the glasses and crack the plates #

414
00:27:10,879 --> 00:27:13,130
# 气得比尔博・巴金斯火冒三丈 #
# That's what Bilbo Baggin hates#

415
00:27:13,381 --> 00:27:14,757
# 衣服撕碎 满地油腻 #
# Cut the cloth, tread on the fat #

416
00:27:15,008 --> 00:27:16,800
# 吃剩骨头 垫子上放 #
# Leave the bones on the bedroom mat #

417
00:27:17,052 --> 00:27:18,510
# 牛奶打开 倒在地上 #
# Pour the milk on the pantry floor #

418
00:27:20,722 --> 00:27:21,805
# 酒渍溅到 #
# Splash the wine #

419
00:27:22,057 --> 00:27:22,723
# 每扇门上 #
# on every door #

420
00:27:22,974 --> 00:27:24,516
# 陶瓷摔碎 扔碗里煮 #
# Dump the crocks in a boiling bowl #

421
00:27:24,768 --> 00:27:26,310
# 拿个棍子 全部打碎 #
# Pound them up with a thumping pole #

422
00:27:26,561 --> 00:27:27,227
# 完事之后 #
# When you're finished #

423
00:27:27,479 --> 00:27:28,520
# 若还完整 #
# If they are whole #

424
00:27:31,650 --> 00:27:33,192
# 全扔客厅 散落一地 #
# Send them down the hall to roll #

425
00:27:41,868 --> 00:27:43,577
# 气得比尔博・巴金斯火冒三丈 #
# That's what Bilbo Baggins hates #

426
00:27:46,623 --> 00:27:48,624
比尔博
Bilbo.

427
00:27:57,592 --> 00:27:59,301
他来了
He is here.

428
00:28:03,348 --> 00:28:04,890
你好 甘道夫
Gandalf.

429
00:28:06,309 --> 00:28:07,101
我记得你说...
I thought you said...

430
00:28:07,352 --> 00:28:08,394
这里很好找...
this place would be easy to find...

431
00:28:08,645 --> 00:28:11,146
但我迷路了 两次
I lost my way, twice.

432
00:28:11,398 --> 00:28:14,817
要不是门上有标记 我绝对找不到这儿
I wouldn't have found it at all had it not been for that mark on the door.

433
00:28:15,068 --> 00:28:17,945
标记? 门上没有标记 一周前刚漆过
Mark? There's no mark on that door. It was painted a week ago.

434
00:28:18,196 --> 00:28:21,198
有的 我标记上去的
There is a mark. I put it there myself.

435
00:28:22,033 --> 00:28:26,120
比尔博・巴金斯 允许我向你介绍这些伙伴的领袖:
Bilbo Baggins, allow me to introduce the leader of our company:

436
00:28:26,705 --> 00:28:28,622
索林・橡木盾
Thorin Oakenshield.

437
00:28:28,873 --> 00:28:30,374
那么...
So...

438
00:28:31,918 --> 00:28:33,627
你就是那个霍比特人
this is the Hobbit.

439
00:28:34,671 --> 00:28:36,964
和我说说 巴金斯先生 以前打过仗吗?
Tell me, Mr. Baggins, have you done much fighting?

440
00:28:37,215 --> 00:28:38,716
- 你说什么?  - 用斧子还是剑?
- Pardon me? Ax or sword?

441
00:28:39,342 --> 00:28:40,801
喜欢用什么武器?
What's your weapon of choice?

442
00:28:41,052 --> 00:28:44,471
呃 非要问的话 我对扔板栗颇有心得...
Well, I do have some skill at conkers, if you must know...

443
00:28:44,723 --> 00:28:48,267
但这有什么联系吗?
but I fail to see why that's relevant.

444
00:28:48,685 --> 00:28:50,227
如我所料
Thought as much.

445
00:28:50,478 --> 00:28:53,230
比起飞贼 他更像个杂货商
He looks more like a grocer than a burglar.

446
00:28:58,486 --> 00:28:59,153
伊瑞德隆会议...
What news...

447
00:28:59,404 --> 00:29:02,156
传来什么消息? 他们都来了吗?
from the meeting in Ered Luin? Did they all come?

448
00:29:02,407 --> 00:29:05,409
- 七个王国的使者都来了  - 全都来了!
- Aye. Envoys from all seven kingdoms.  - All of them!

449
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:08,203
铁丘陵的矮人怎么说?
And what did the Dwarves of the Iron Hills say?

450
00:29:09,372 --> 00:29:11,290
戴因来吗?
Is Dain with us?

451
00:29:13,668 --> 00:29:15,085
他们不愿意来
They will not come.

452
00:29:18,214 --> 00:29:19,214
他们说这次探险...
They say this quest...

453
00:29:19,466 --> 00:29:22,634
仅仅是我们自己的事
is ours and ours alone.

454
00:29:24,804 --> 00:29:27,347
你们要去探险?
You're going on a quest?

455
00:29:28,016 --> 00:29:32,853
比尔博 亲爱的伙计 再多点几盏灯吧
Bilbo, my dear fellow, let us have a little more light.

456
00:29:33,855 --> 00:29:35,606
在遥远的东方...
Far to the east...

457
00:29:36,232 --> 00:29:38,984
穿越无数的山脉河流...
over ranges and rivers...

458
00:29:39,277 --> 00:29:42,529
跨过无尽的森林和荒漠...
beyond woodlands and wastelands...

459
00:29:42,781 --> 00:29:45,073
有一座孤峰傲立着
lies a single, solitary peak.

460
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:50,412
"孤山"
"The Lonely Mountain."

461
00:29:51,039 --> 00:29:53,123
没错 欧因读到过...
Aye, Oin has read...

462
00:29:53,374 --> 00:29:57,711
预言的征兆 征兆显示时机已到
the portents, and the portents say it is time.

463
00:29:58,046 --> 00:29:59,046
如预言所述...
Ravens have been seen...

464
00:29:59,297 --> 00:30:02,841
渡鸦飞回山中
flying back to the mountain, as it was foretold.

465
00:30:03,092 --> 00:30:05,636
"昔日的鸟儿回归...
"When the birds of yore return...

466
00:30:05,887 --> 00:30:06,970
伊鲁柏之时...
to Erebor...

467
00:30:07,222 --> 00:30:08,722
魔兽的统治...
the reign of the beast...

468
00:30:08,973 --> 00:30:10,641
将会结束"
will end. "

469
00:30:13,770 --> 00:30:15,729
- 什么魔兽?  - 指的是...
- Uh, what beast?  - That would be a reference...

470
00:30:16,147 --> 00:30:17,397
恐惧之王史矛革...
to Smaug the Terrible...

471
00:30:17,649 --> 00:30:18,899
我们时代...
chiefest and greatest...

472
00:30:19,150 --> 00:30:20,275
最可怕的灾难
calamity of our age.

473
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:23,987
会飞的喷火者
Airborne fire-breather.

474
00:30:24,239 --> 00:30:25,239
剃刀般尖锐的牙齿...
Teeth like razors...

475
00:30:25,490 --> 00:30:26,949
肉钩一样的爪子
claws like meat hooks.

476
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,492
极度喜爱贵重金属
Fond of precious metals.

477
00:30:28,743 --> 00:30:29,618
我知道龙长啥样
I know what a dragon is.

478
00:30:30,203 --> 00:30:31,912
我才不怕 我准备好了
I'm not afraid. I'm up for it.

479
00:30:32,163 --> 00:30:34,915
我要让他的菊花好好尝尝矮人钢铁的厉害!
I'll give him a taste of Dwarfish iron right up his jacksie!

480
00:30:35,166 --> 00:30:35,833
好小子 欧力!
Good lad, Ori!

481
00:30:36,084 --> 00:30:36,750
坐下
Sit down.

482
00:30:37,001 --> 00:30:38,168
即使整支军队出动...
The task would be difficult...

483
00:30:38,419 --> 00:30:39,795
任务也很艰巨...
with an army behind us...

484
00:30:40,046 --> 00:30:42,130
何况我们只有13个人
but we number just 13.

485
00:30:42,382 --> 00:30:44,258
而且其中还有歪瓜裂枣...
And not 13 of the best...

486
00:30:44,884 --> 00:30:46,176
傻头傻脑的
nor brightest.

487
00:30:46,511 --> 00:30:48,303
喂 你说谁傻瓜呢?
Hey, who are you calling dim?

488
00:30:48,847 --> 00:30:50,305
不好意思 他刚说什么?
Sorry, what did he say?

489
00:30:50,557 --> 00:30:52,432
我们虽然人少...
We may be few in number...

490
00:30:53,226 --> 00:30:56,228
但我们是战士 所有人...
but we're fighters, all of us...

491
00:30:56,479 --> 00:30:57,479
都会奋战到底
to the last Dwarf.

492
00:30:57,730 --> 00:30:59,898
你们还忘了 我们有巫师结伴
And you forget, we have a Wizard in our company.

493
00:31:00,149 --> 00:31:01,942
甘道夫可以杀掉上百条龙
Gandalf will have killed hundreds of dragons.

494
00:31:02,735 --> 00:31:04,653
这个 我不敢说...
Oh, well, no. I wouldn't say...

495
00:31:04,904 --> 00:31:06,822
- 那有多少?  - 什么?
- How many, then?  - What?

496
00:31:07,073 --> 00:31:08,323
你杀过多少条龙?
How many dragons have you killed?

497
00:31:11,411 --> 00:31:12,286
说啊
Go on.

498
00:31:12,537 --> 00:31:13,787
给个数
Give us a number.

499
00:31:16,416 --> 00:31:17,457
拜托 别吵了
Excuse me. Please.

500
00:31:22,422 --> 00:31:23,797
如果我们能看见这些预兆...
If we have read these signs...

501
00:31:24,048 --> 00:31:26,675
难道别的种族就看不出来吗?
do you not think others will have read them too?

502
00:31:29,012 --> 00:31:31,555
谣言已经传开
Rumors have begun to spread.

503
00:31:31,973 --> 00:31:34,641
那巨龙史矛革已经有60年无人见过
The dragon, Smaug, has not been seen for 60 years.

504
00:31:36,311 --> 00:31:38,562
许多人都觊觎着东方那片土地 思索...
Eyes look east to the mountain, assessing...

505
00:31:39,439 --> 00:31:42,733
徘徊 权衡利弊
wondering, weighing the risk.

506
00:31:43,151 --> 00:31:45,527
或许我们的宝藏现在无人看守
Perhaps the vast wealth of our people now lies unprotected.

507
00:31:46,154 --> 00:31:49,615
我们是坐视别人抢走我们的东西?
Do we sit back while others claim what is rightfully ours?

508
00:31:50,325 --> 00:31:52,034
还是抓住机会...
Or do we seize this chance...

509
00:31:52,493 --> 00:31:53,201
夺回伊鲁柏?
to take back Erebor?

510
00:31:55,496 --> 00:31:58,290
可是 要塞的正门被堵死了
You forget, the Front Gate is sealed.

511
00:31:58,708 --> 00:31:59,583
已经没有路...
There is no way...

512
00:31:59,834 --> 00:32:01,710
可以进山了
into the mountain.

513
00:32:01,961 --> 00:32:05,213
这可未必 亲爱的巴林
That, my dear Balin, is not entirely true.

514
00:32:09,260 --> 00:32:10,677
你怎么会有这个?
How came you by this?

515
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:12,220
是你父亲...
It was given to me...

516
00:32:12,472 --> 00:32:14,056
给我的
by your father.

517
00:32:14,307 --> 00:32:15,807
索恩给我的
By Thrain.

518
00:32:16,059 --> 00:32:17,559
要我保管
For safekeeping.

519
00:32:18,394 --> 00:32:19,102
现在...
It is yours...

520
00:32:19,354 --> 00:32:20,437
是你的了
now.

521
00:32:27,862 --> 00:32:29,279
如果有钥匙...
If there is a key...

522
00:32:30,281 --> 00:32:31,865
肯定就有门
there must be a door.

523
00:32:32,492 --> 00:32:33,158
这些符语...
These runes...

524
00:32:33,409 --> 00:32:36,954
暗示有个密门通向要塞大厅
speak of a hidden passage to the Lower Halls.

525
00:32:37,205 --> 00:32:39,289
有别的方法进去
There's another way in.

526
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:43,293
能找到最好 但矮人的门关着的时候看不见
Well, if we can find it, but Dwarf doors are invisible when closed.

527
00:32:45,672 --> 00:32:48,465
位置就在这张地图上...
The answer lies hidden somewhere in this map...

528
00:32:48,716 --> 00:32:50,676
但是我不知道如何找到它
and I do not have the skill to find it.

529
00:32:50,927 --> 00:32:54,096
但是中土世界有人可以
But there are others in Middle-earth who can.

530
00:32:56,057 --> 00:32:59,351
我想的计划需要做的非常隐蔽...
The task I have in mind will require a great deal of stealth...

531
00:32:59,602 --> 00:33:01,645
并且需要巨大的勇气
and no small amount of courage.

532
00:33:03,439 --> 00:33:07,567
如果我们够细心够机灵 我相信是可以做到的
But if we are careful and clever, I believe that it can be done.

533
00:33:07,819 --> 00:33:09,319
所以我们需要一个飞贼
That's why we need a burglar.

534
00:33:09,696 --> 00:33:13,115
要一个本领高强的飞贼 最好是专家
Hmm. And a good one too. An expert, I'd imagine.

535
00:33:13,366 --> 00:33:15,617
你是吗?
And are you?

536
00:33:18,079 --> 00:33:19,454
我是什么?
Am I what?

537
00:33:19,706 --> 00:33:22,416
他说他就是一个专家
He said he's an expert.

538
00:33:22,959 --> 00:33:27,754
我? 不不 我不是飞贼 我这辈子从未偷过东西
Me? No. No, no, no. I'm not a burglar. I've never stolen a thing in my life.

539
00:33:28,006 --> 00:33:30,632
我也同意巴金斯先生
Well, I'm afraid I have to agree with Mr. Baggins.

540
00:33:30,883 --> 00:33:32,843
他绝对不是当飞贼的料
He's hardly burglar material.

541
00:33:33,094 --> 00:33:34,052
不是
Nope.

542
00:33:34,762 --> 00:33:38,515
是啊 既不会战斗也不会防御的软弱之人无法在野外生存
Aye, the Wild is no place for gentle folk who can neither fight nor fend for themselves.

543
00:33:38,766 --> 00:33:40,600
他也就一般
He's just fine.

544
00:33:46,190 --> 00:33:47,357
够了!
Enough!

545
00:33:47,608 --> 00:33:49,151
我说比尔博・巴金斯是...
If I say Bilbo Baggins...

546
00:33:49,402 --> 00:33:50,861
飞贼 那他...
is a burglar, then a burglar...

547
00:33:51,112 --> 00:33:52,529
就是
he is.

548
00:33:54,115 --> 00:33:55,323
霍比特人的脚步轻盈...
Hobbits are light on their feet...

549
00:33:55,575 --> 00:33:59,703
如果他们想 大多数人都注意不到他们
In fact, they can pass unseen by most, if they choose.

550
00:33:59,954 --> 00:34:03,498
虽然龙对于矮人气味十分熟悉...
And, while the dragon is accustomed to the smell of Dwarf...

551
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:07,205
但是霍比特人的气息 它就完全不了解...
the scent of a Hobbit is all but unknown to him...

552
00:34:07,364 --> 00:34:10,538
这会给我们带来很大优势
which gives us a distinct advantage.

553
00:34:10,700 --> 00:34:12,626
你让我寻找第14名成员
You asked me to find the 14th member of this

554
00:34:12,626 --> 00:34:15,126
我推荐巴金斯先生
company and I have chosen Mr. Baggins.

555
00:34:15,413 --> 00:34:18,383
他还是很能干的 别被外表迷惑了
There's a lot more to him than appearances suggest.

556
00:34:18,541 --> 00:34:21,385
他所能做的 完全超乎你们得想象
And he's got a great deal more to offer than any of you know.

557
00:34:22,963 --> 00:34:24,306
他自己也不知道
Including himself.

558
00:34:30,053 --> 00:34:32,556
在这点上 你得相信我
You must trust me on this.

559
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:36,897
好吧
Very well.

560
00:34:37,269 --> 00:34:38,816
- 就按你的来做  - 不 不
- We will do it your way.  - No, no.

561
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:41,443
- 把合同给他  - 算我们一个
- Give him the contract.  - We're in. We're off.

562
00:34:41,606 --> 00:34:42,653
这是惯例条款
It's just the usual.

563
00:34:42,816 --> 00:34:44,818
包括总体支出...
Summary of out-of-pocket expenses...

564
00:34:44,985 --> 00:34:46,578
所需时间 报酬...
time required, remuneration...

565
00:34:46,945 --> 00:34:48,618
葬礼安排 等等
funeral arrangements, so forth.

566
00:34:49,614 --> 00:34:50,991
葬礼安排?
Funeral arrangements?

567
00:34:56,788 --> 00:34:58,290
我可不能保证他小命安全
I cannot guarantee his safety.

568
00:34:58,999 --> 00:35:00,251
了解
Understood.

569
00:35:00,709 --> 00:35:03,258
未来我也不会照顾他
Nor will I be responsible for his fate.

570
00:35:07,173 --> 00:35:08,470
同意
Agreed.

571
00:35:08,633 --> 00:35:08,939
"条款: 事成付款
"Terms: Cash on

572
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:13,184
报酬将达到并不超过总收益的十四分之一 如果有收益"
delivery, up to but not exceeding one-fourteenth of total profit, if any."

573
00:35:13,388 --> 00:35:15,265
很公平
Hmm. Seems fair.

574
00:35:15,432 --> 00:35:19,153
"本队将不对成员未来所受的各种伤负责...
"Present company shall not be liable for injuries inflicted by...

575
00:35:19,311 --> 00:35:24,568
这些伤害包括但不局限于撕裂伤...
or sustained as a consequence thereof, including, but not limited to lacerations...

576
00:35:25,984 --> 00:35:27,657
内脏伤..."
evisceration..."

577
00:35:30,322 --> 00:35:31,323
火葬?
Incineration?

578
00:35:31,489 --> 00:35:34,459
对 那龙也许眨眼间就把你的血肉全部烧了
Aye. He'll melt the flesh off your bones in the blink of an eye.

579
00:35:39,706 --> 00:35:42,630
- 你没事吧?  - 嗯? 我很好
- You all right, laddie?  - Huh? Yeah.

580
00:35:44,377 --> 00:35:45,720
头有点晕
Feel a bit faint.

581
00:35:46,087 --> 00:35:48,055
- 想象一下会飞的火炉  - 新鲜空气
- Think furnace with wings.  - Air.

582
00:35:48,214 --> 00:35:49,716
我需要缓口气
I need air.

583
00:35:49,883 --> 00:35:52,477
炽烈的亮光 灼烧的疼痛 然后噗的一下
Flash of light, searing pain, then poof.

584
00:35:52,635 --> 00:35:54,637
你就成了一堆炭灰了
You're nothing more than a pile of ash.

585
00:36:01,019 --> 00:36:02,020
不好
Nope.

586
00:36:03,229 --> 00:36:05,106
你真会帮倒忙 波佛
Oh, very helpful, Bofur.

587
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:08,034
我没事的 让我安静的待会就行了
I'll be all right. Just let me sit quietly for a moment.

588
00:36:08,193 --> 00:36:11,538
你太沉溺于这种安逸的生活了
You've been sitting quietly for far too long.

589
00:36:11,863 --> 00:36:15,993
你怎么对那些杯垫和你老妈的碟子...
Tell me, when did doilies and your mother's dishes...

590
00:36:16,201 --> 00:36:17,828
看得如此重要?
become so important to you?

591
00:36:18,370 --> 00:36:20,471
我记忆中的那个小霍比特人总是
I remember a young Hobbit who was always

592
00:36:20,471 --> 00:36:23,171
在林子间寻找精灵们
running off in search of Elves in the woods.

593
00:36:23,375 --> 00:36:26,549
总是玩到很晚回家...
Who would stay out late, come home after dark...

594
00:36:26,711 --> 00:36:30,341
全身都是泥巴 树枝 还有萤火虫
trailing mud and twigs and fireflies.

595
00:36:30,507 --> 00:36:32,885
那个年轻的霍比特人 总是想要...
A young Hobbit who would have liked nothing better...

596
00:36:33,093 --> 00:36:36,518
探索夏尔外面的世界
than to find out what was beyond the borders of the Shire.

597
00:36:37,180 --> 00:36:40,935
世界可不是一本书或是一张地图
The world is not in your books and maps.

598
00:36:42,227 --> 00:36:44,150
它在屋外
It's out there.

599
00:36:45,855 --> 00:36:48,108
我不能就这样无声无息地和你们走
I can't just go running off into the blue.

600
00:36:48,274 --> 00:36:51,448
我是住在袋底洞的巴金斯
I am a Baggins of Bag-end.

601
00:36:51,569 --> 00:36:53,742
但你也是图克家族的
You are also a Took.

602
00:36:55,698 --> 00:36:59,077
你知道吗 你的曾曾曾曾伯父 吼牛・图克...
Did you know that your great-great-great-great-uncle Bullroarer Took...

603
00:36:59,244 --> 00:37:01,872
体型大得能够骑一匹马吗?
was so large, he could ride a real horse?

604
00:37:02,080 --> 00:37:04,208
- 知道  - 当然 他可以
- Yes.  - Yes, well, he could.

605
00:37:04,374 --> 00:37:07,253
绿原之战中 他冲向哥布林大军
In the Battle of Green Fields, he charged the Goblin ranks.

606
00:37:07,419 --> 00:37:11,265
他的力量之大 用棒子生生把敌方国王脑袋敲下来...
He swung his club so hard, it knocked the Goblin king's head clean off...

607
00:37:11,423 --> 00:37:15,599
滚了一百多码才掉到一个兔子窝里
and it sailed 100 yards through the air and went down a rabbit hole.

608
00:37:15,844 --> 00:37:17,517
他们赢得了战役
And thus, the battle was won.

609
00:37:18,304 --> 00:37:21,308
从那以后 有人因此发明了高尔夫(哥布林国王名叫高尔夫裘)
And the game of golf invented at the same time.

610
00:37:24,436 --> 00:37:26,655
我知道你是乱编的
I do believe you made that up.

611
00:37:26,813 --> 00:37:30,568
所有精彩的故事都需要润润色嘛
Well, all good stories deserve embellishment.

612
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:36,081
如果你回来了 那你也有自己的传奇故事了
You'll have a tale or two to tell of your own when you come back.

613
00:37:39,826 --> 00:37:42,045
你能保证我能安全回来?
Can you promise that I will come back?

614
00:37:43,997 --> 00:37:45,499
不能
No.

615
00:37:45,707 --> 00:37:47,755
如果你能回得来...
And if you do...

616
00:37:48,585 --> 00:37:50,883
你绝对不会和现在一样
you will not be the same.

617
00:37:52,464 --> 00:37:54,216
我也同意
That's what I thought.

618
00:37:55,383 --> 00:37:58,432
不好意思 甘道夫 我不能签这个
Sorry, Gandalf, I can't sign this.

619
00:37:59,971 --> 00:38:02,224
你找错霍比特人了
You've got the wrong Hobbit.

620
00:38:08,646 --> 00:38:12,276
我们的飞贼似乎不干了
It appears we have lost our burglar.

621
00:38:13,318 --> 00:38:15,320
也许这样也好
Probably for the best.

622
00:38:15,487 --> 00:38:17,865
事事总不能如意啊
The odds were always against us.

623
00:38:18,031 --> 00:38:21,035
说到底 我们是什么?
After all, what are we?

624
00:38:21,534 --> 00:38:24,378
商人 矿工...
Merchants, miners...

625
00:38:24,996 --> 00:38:27,169
铁匠 做玩具的
tinkers, toy-makers.

626
00:38:27,332 --> 00:38:30,302
看起来不太像是一群英雄们
Heh, heh. Hardly the stuff of legend.

627
00:38:30,793 --> 00:38:33,637
我们中间还是有战士的
There are a few warriors amongst us.

628
00:38:34,297 --> 00:38:36,174
残兵败将
Old warriors.

629
00:38:36,341 --> 00:38:38,719
比起铁丘陵的矮人军队
I would take each and every one of these Dwarves...

630
00:38:38,843 --> 00:38:41,016
我宁可有这些人的追随
over an army from the Iron Hills.

631
00:38:41,221 --> 00:38:44,145
因为在我号召时他们一定能回应
For when I called upon them, they answered.

632
00:38:44,891 --> 00:38:47,485
忠诚 荣耀...
Loyalty, honor...

633
00:38:47,894 --> 00:38:49,692
热诚
a willing heart.

634
00:38:51,314 --> 00:38:53,908
我觉得这些就够了
I can ask no more than that.

635
00:38:54,484 --> 00:38:56,657
你不必亲自去
You don't have to do this.

636
00:38:57,070 --> 00:38:58,697
你可以选择不去
You have a choice.

637
00:38:58,863 --> 00:39:01,867
我们族人拥戴你 愿意受你领导
You've done honorably by our people.

638
00:39:02,700 --> 00:39:06,500
是你在蓝山开辟新的居住地
You have built a new life for us in the Blue Mountains.

639
00:39:06,829 --> 00:39:09,833
过着和平富裕的生活
A life of peace and plenty.

640
00:39:10,667 --> 00:39:15,639
我觉得这一切比伊鲁柏的金子更宝贵
A life that is worth more than all the gold in Erebor.

641
00:39:16,172 --> 00:39:21,099
从我的爷爷传到我父亲 现在到我了
From my grandfather to my father, this has come to me.

642
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:26,600
他们无时无刻都在想着矮人能重夺自己的故乡
They dreamt of the day when the Dwarves of Erebor would reclaim their homeland.

643
00:39:28,434 --> 00:39:30,903
没有其他选择 巴林
There is no choice, Balin.

644
00:39:32,355 --> 00:39:33,902
我别无选择
Not for me.

645
00:39:36,276 --> 00:39:37,949
那么 我们将与你同生共死
Then we are with you, laddie.

646
00:39:39,904 --> 00:39:42,248
我们会成功的
We will see it done.

647
00:40:04,304 --> 00:40:11,859
# 登上远山冰寒之巅 #
# Far over the misty mountains cold #

648
00:40:13,271 --> 00:40:17,401
# 深入地牢深渊之底 #
# To dungeons deep #

649
00:40:17,775 --> 00:40:21,780
# 探索古老洞窟之中 #
# And caverns old #

650
00:40:22,447 --> 00:40:26,577
# 在太阳升起之前 #
# We must away #

651
00:40:27,160 --> 00:40:31,256
# 我们必须整装出发 #
# 'Ere break of day #

652
00:40:31,497 --> 00:40:39,497
# 去追寻那遗落之财 #
# To find our long-forgotten gold #

653
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:48,840
# 高处的松树在低吼 #
# The pines were roaring on the height #

654
00:40:49,891 --> 00:40:57,891
# 夜晚的寒风在呼啸 #
# The winds were moaning in the night #

655
00:40:58,858 --> 00:41:06,858
# 希望之火 传播不息 #
# The fire was red, it flaming spread #

656
00:41:08,076 --> 00:41:15,676
# 光明从这火中而来 #
# The trees like torches blazed with light #

657
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:57,758
早啊?
Hello?

658
00:42:07,885 --> 00:42:09,057
好样的
Yes.

659
00:42:09,595 --> 00:42:12,064
不错
Yes.

660
00:43:23,544 --> 00:43:25,967
比尔博先生 你这是去哪儿?
Here, Mr. Bilbo, where are you off to?

661
00:43:26,130 --> 00:43:28,883
- 不能停下说 我已经迟到了!  - 什么迟到?
- Can't stop, I'm already late!  - Late for what?

662
00:43:29,175 --> 00:43:32,145
我要去冒险!
I'm going on an adventure!

663
00:43:37,683 --> 00:43:41,108
我说过的 我说过吗? 这一趟来得不值啊
I said it. Didn't I say it? Coming here was a waste of time.

664
00:43:41,270 --> 00:43:42,817
你说的没错
That's true enough.

665
00:43:43,022 --> 00:43:45,946
这主意太荒唐了 霍比特人? 半身人(通用语中对霍比特人的称呼)?
Ridiculous notion. Use a Hobbit? A Halfling?

666
00:43:47,693 --> 00:43:48,694
等等!
Wait!

667
00:43:49,612 --> 00:43:50,659
等下我!
Wait!

668
00:44:01,874 --> 00:44:03,467
我签名了
I signed it.

669
00:44:05,169 --> 00:44:06,466
给
Here.

670
00:44:15,805 --> 00:44:18,308
很好 一切都按程序填写
Everything appears to be in order.

671
00:44:18,474 --> 00:44:20,852
欢迎 巴金斯大师...
Welcome, Master Baggins...

672
00:44:21,519 --> 00:44:25,069
欢迎加入索林・橡木盾小队
to the company of Thorin Oakenshield.

673
00:44:30,444 --> 00:44:31,616
给他一匹马崽子
Give him a pony.

674
00:44:32,071 --> 00:44:33,664
哦 不用这么麻烦了
No, no, that won't be necessary.

675
00:44:33,823 --> 00:44:36,042
谢了 我自信我能赶上你们步伐
Thank you. I'm sure I can keep up on foot.

676
00:44:36,200 --> 00:44:38,749
我经常出去徒步旅游的 知道吗?
I've done my fair share of walking holidays, you know?

677
00:44:38,953 --> 00:44:41,001
有一次还跑到蛙村去了
Even got as far as Frogmorton once.

678
00:44:54,886 --> 00:44:56,763
快点 诺力 给钱
Come on, Nori. Pay up.

679
00:44:58,764 --> 00:45:00,858
- 还有一袋  - 谢了 小子
- One more.  - Thanks, lad.

680
00:45:01,017 --> 00:45:02,610
这是干嘛?
What's that about?

681
00:45:02,727 --> 00:45:07,324
哦 他们在打赌 赌你会不会回心转意
Oh, they took wagers on whether or not you'd turn up.

682
00:45:07,481 --> 00:45:10,325
大多数人赌你不会
Most of them bet that you wouldn't.

683
00:45:11,694 --> 00:45:13,287
你觉得呢?
And what did you think?

684
00:45:18,075 --> 00:45:22,672
我的好朋友 我从未怀疑过你
My dear fellow, I never doubted you for a second.

685
00:45:27,543 --> 00:45:31,468
这马毛让我过敏了
It's horse hair. Having a reaction.

686
00:45:33,090 --> 00:45:34,717
不不 等下
No, wait, wait, stop.

687
00:45:35,343 --> 00:45:37,437
停下! 我们得回头
Stop! We have to turn around.

688
00:45:37,762 --> 00:45:39,764
到底怎么啦?
What on earth is the matter?

689
00:45:39,889 --> 00:45:42,108
- 我忘记带我的手帕了  - 给你
- I forgot my handkerchief.  - Here.

690
00:45:43,768 --> 00:45:44,769
用这个
Use this.

691
00:45:49,231 --> 00:45:50,699
继续行进
Move on.

692
00:45:57,865 --> 00:46:00,664
你得习惯不带手帕的生活...
You'll have to manage without pocket handkerchiefs...

693
00:46:00,868 --> 00:46:03,212
还有很多其他的事情 比尔博・巴金斯...
and a good many other things, Bilbo Baggins...

694
00:46:03,329 --> 00:46:06,754
直到这趟旅程结束
before we reach our journey's end.

695
00:46:07,416 --> 00:46:12,764
你在夏尔的丘陵与小河边长大
You were born to the rolling hills and little rivers of the Shire.

696
00:46:13,798 --> 00:46:16,677
但如今家园已在身后
But home is now behind you.

697
00:46:16,842 --> 00:46:19,971
世界尽在眼前
The world is ahead.

698
00:47:00,678 --> 00:47:04,057
嗨 姑娘 真是个好姑娘!
Hello, girl. Who's a good girl?

699
00:47:07,601 --> 00:47:09,524
这是我俩的小秘密 桃金娘
It's our little secret, Myrtle.

700
00:47:09,687 --> 00:47:11,655
谁也不许告诉 嘘 嘘
You must tell no one. Shh, shh.

701
00:47:16,402 --> 00:47:17,449
那是什么?
What was that?

702
00:47:18,821 --> 00:47:19,868
是半兽人
Orcs.

703
00:47:20,573 --> 00:47:21,574
半兽人?
Orcs?

704
00:47:23,284 --> 00:47:26,208
是些嗜杀成性的家伙 外头起码有几十个
Throat-cutters. There'll be dozens of them out there.

705
00:47:26,704 --> 00:47:28,502
在孤土到处可见它们的身影(孤土西起蓝山 东至迷雾山脉)
The lone-lands are crawling with them.

706
00:47:28,664 --> 00:47:31,543
他们总在凌晨时分 人们熟睡时动手
They strike in the wee small hours when everyone's asleep.

707
00:47:31,709 --> 00:47:34,883
干脆利落 人们来不及尖叫 就已血流成河
Quick and quiet, no screams. Just lots of blood.

708
00:47:39,425 --> 00:47:41,098
你们以为这些很好玩?
You think that's funny?

709
00:47:43,054 --> 00:47:45,432
你们以为被半兽人夜袭是个玩笑?
You think a night raid by Orcs is a joke?

710
00:47:46,223 --> 00:47:47,645
我们不是这个意思
We didn't mean anything by it.

711
00:47:48,809 --> 00:47:50,607
是啊 你们不是这个意思
No, you didn't.

712
00:47:50,936 --> 00:47:53,234
你们对这世界根本一无所知
You know nothing of the world.

713
00:47:54,857 --> 00:47:57,110
别介意 小家伙
Don't mind him, laddie.

714
00:47:57,276 --> 00:48:01,998
索林比任何人都更有理由痛恨半兽人
Thorin has more cause than most to hate Orcs.

715
00:48:06,827 --> 00:48:09,876
在恶龙占领孤山后...
After the dragon took the Lonely Mountain...

716
00:48:10,081 --> 00:48:15,884
国王索尔曾试图收复古老的矮人王国 摩瑞亚
King Thror tried to reclaim the ancient Dwarf kingdom of Moria.

717
00:48:17,755 --> 00:48:21,100
但敌人早已捷足先登
But our enemy had got there first.

718
00:48:33,395 --> 00:48:37,445
摩瑞亚被半兽人军团占领...
Moria had been taken by legions of Orcs...

719
00:48:37,608 --> 00:48:42,330
领头的是它们族群中最邪恶的家伙
led by the most vile of all their race:

720
00:48:42,780 --> 00:48:45,909
毁灭者阿索格
Azog the Defiler.

721
00:48:48,202 --> 00:48:50,921
这个身形巨大的刚达巴半兽人
The giant Gundabad Orc...

722
00:48:51,372 --> 00:48:56,344
曾发誓要杀尽杜林一族
had sworn to wipe out the line of Durin.

723
00:49:00,548 --> 00:49:02,300
他一出手...
He began...

724
00:49:03,384 --> 00:49:05,261
就砍下了国王的脑袋
by beheading the king.

725
00:49:16,647 --> 00:49:19,491
不!
No!

726
00:49:20,693 --> 00:49:25,540
索林的父亲索恩悲伤得几乎发狂
Thrain, Thorin's father, was driven mad by grief.

727
00:49:25,698 --> 00:49:28,326
他失踪了 也许被俘 也许被杀...
He went missing. Taken prisoner or killed...

728
00:49:28,993 --> 00:49:31,087
我们无从知晓
We did not know.

729
00:49:31,954 --> 00:49:33,422
我们失去了首领
We were leaderless.

730
00:49:34,165 --> 00:49:37,715
失败与死亡...
Defeat and death...

731
00:49:37,877 --> 00:49:39,720
正步步紧逼
were upon us.

732
00:49:42,673 --> 00:49:46,519
就在那时我看到了他
That is when I saw him.

733
00:49:48,762 --> 00:49:50,480
一位年轻的矮人王子...
A young Dwarf prince...

734
00:49:51,473 --> 00:49:55,068
力战苍白半兽人
facing down the pale Orc.

735
00:49:59,315 --> 00:50:02,910
他孤身与强敌血战
He stood alone against this terrible foe.

736
00:50:12,661 --> 00:50:14,254
他的盔甲碎了...
His armor rent...

737
00:50:14,455 --> 00:50:17,925
只能挥舞着一截橡木当盾牌
wielding nothing but an oaken branch as a shield.

738
00:50:31,013 --> 00:50:35,644
那一天 毁灭者阿索格明白了...
Azog the Defiler learned that day...

739
00:50:36,268 --> 00:50:40,569
杜林族系绝不会轻易瓦解
that the line of Durin would not be so easily broken.

740
00:50:43,768 --> 00:50:46,469
为荣誉

741
00:50:48,068 --> 00:50:52,069
给我杀!

742
00:51:08,550 --> 00:51:10,052
我们集结了军力
Our forces rallied...

743
00:51:11,303 --> 00:51:13,772
击退了半兽人
and drove the Orcs back.

744
00:51:15,641 --> 00:51:16,938
我们的敌人...
And our enemy...

745
00:51:17,768 --> 00:51:19,736
被打败了
had been defeated.

746
00:51:21,230 --> 00:51:23,574
但那一晚既没有庆宴...
But there was no feast...

747
00:51:24,275 --> 00:51:27,028
也没有歌声...
nor song that night...

748
00:51:27,194 --> 00:51:31,995
因为我们的伤亡太过惨重
for our dead were beyond the count of grief.

749
00:51:33,075 --> 00:51:36,420
只有极少数得以存活
We few had survived.

750
00:51:43,585 --> 00:51:46,509
于是我告诉自己...
And I thought to myself then...

751
00:51:49,258 --> 00:51:53,604
还有这样一个人值得我去追随
there is one who I could follow.

752
00:51:55,764 --> 00:51:57,858
还有这样一个人...
There is one...

753
00:51:58,642 --> 00:52:00,610
我愿视为王
I could call king.

754
00:52:19,580 --> 00:52:20,877
那苍白半兽人呢?
And the pale Orc?

755
00:52:23,292 --> 00:52:24,760
他后来怎么样了?
What happened to him?

756
00:52:24,918 --> 00:52:28,468
他溜回了起兵的那个洞里
He slunk back into the hole whence he came.

757
00:52:28,922 --> 00:52:32,517
早就因伤势过重死了
That filth died of his wounds long ago.

758
00:52:55,692 --> 00:52:58,517
向大王汇报...

759
00:52:59,522 --> 00:53:02,947
我们找到了该死的矮人

760
00:53:18,597 --> 00:53:22,227
喂 甘道夫先生 这水漫金山的你就不能想想办法吗?
Here, Mr. Gandalf, can't you do something about this deluge?

761
00:53:22,851 --> 00:53:25,274
这是在下雨 矮人大人...
It is raining, Master Dwarf...

762
00:53:25,437 --> 00:53:29,158
想止住雨的唯一办法就是等雨自己停下来
and it will continue to rain until the rain is done.

763
00:53:29,733 --> 00:53:33,783
如果你想改变这世界上的天气 那恐怕得找别的巫师了
If you wish to change the weather of the world, you should find yourself another Wizard.

764
00:53:35,447 --> 00:53:36,744
- 有别的吗?  - 别的什么?
- Are there any?  - What?

765
00:53:36,907 --> 00:53:39,535
- 别的巫师  - 像我们这样的人有五个
- Other Wizards.  - There are five of us.

766
00:53:39,701 --> 00:53:44,207
其中最位高权重的是白袍萨鲁曼
The greatest of our order is Saruman the White.

767
00:53:44,415 --> 00:53:46,884
接下来是两位蓝袍巫师...
Then there are the two Blue Wizards...

768
00:53:48,210 --> 00:53:50,588
不过我已经忘了他们的名字了
Do you know, I've quite forgotten their names.

769
00:53:51,755 --> 00:53:52,972
那第五个呢?
And who is the fifth?

770
00:53:53,173 --> 00:53:57,144
是褐袍瑞达加斯特
Well, that would be Radagast the Brown.

771
00:53:57,302 --> 00:54:01,057
他是个厉害的巫师吗? 还是和你差不多的?
Is he a great Wizard? Or is he more like you?

772
00:54:03,142 --> 00:54:07,818
我想他自有他厉害的地方
I think he's a very great Wizard, in his own way.

773
00:54:08,313 --> 00:54:12,614
他心地温和 偏爱与动物为伴
He's a gentle soul who prefers the company of animals to others.

774
00:54:12,776 --> 00:54:15,825
始终盯防着东部的...
He keeps a watchful eye over the vast forest lands...

775
00:54:16,029 --> 00:54:18,578
广阔森林地带 这是件好事
to the east. And a good thing too.

776
00:54:18,740 --> 00:54:23,792
因为邪恶势力总会试图在世上寻找立足之地
For always evil will look to find a foothold in this world.

777
00:54:30,294 --> 00:54:33,468
不妙 大事不妙了
Not good. Not good at all.

778
00:54:40,846 --> 00:54:42,189
唷
Eww.

779
00:54:57,613 --> 00:54:59,957
哦 不 塞巴斯蒂安
Oh, no. Sebastian.

780
00:55:03,660 --> 00:55:04,707
我的天哪
Good gracious.

781
00:55:25,599 --> 00:55:26,646
快点
Come on.

782
00:55:26,808 --> 00:55:29,903
退后! 给它点新鲜空气 拜托了
Move back! Give him some air, for goodness sake.

783
00:55:39,821 --> 00:55:41,494
来 给
There. There.

784
00:55:42,824 --> 00:55:45,498
我不明白为什么不起作用
I don't understand why it's not working.

785
00:55:45,661 --> 00:55:48,130
这又不是巫术
It's not as if it's witchcraft.

786
00:55:51,124 --> 00:55:53,422
巫术
Witchcraft.

787
00:55:54,503 --> 00:55:58,599
哦 但它确实是巫术
Oh, but it is.

788
00:55:59,508 --> 00:56:05,186
一种邪恶 强大的魔法
A dark and powerful magic.

789
00:56:45,808 --> 00:56:49,586
让这动物免于诅咒
Lerya laman naiquentallo.

790
00:56:50,008 --> 00:56:53,186
现在聆听我的声音
Si a hlare omaquettar.

791
00:56:53,708 --> 00:56:56,786
让其重新焕发生机
Na coilerya en-vinyanta.

792
00:56:58,708 --> 00:57:02,386
现在聆听我的声音
Si a hlare omaquettar.

793
00:57:03,008 --> 00:57:10,686
让其重新焕发生机
Na coilerya en-vinyanta.

794
00:57:36,980 --> 00:57:41,531
那些肮脏的生物究竟是从哪里来的?
Where on this good earth did those foul creatures come from?

795
00:57:43,779 --> 00:57:45,452
古要塞?
The old fortress?

796
00:57:46,073 --> 00:57:47,245
带我去
Show me.

797
00:58:20,816 --> 00:58:22,568
我们今晚在这里扎营
We'll camp here for the night.

798
00:58:23,068 --> 00:58:27,448
菲力 奇力 照看好马儿 和它们待在一块
Fili, Kili, look after the ponies. Make sure you stay with them.

799
00:58:27,698 --> 00:58:31,748
这里以前住着一户农民
A farmer and his family used to live here.

800
00:58:31,910 --> 00:58:34,709
- 欧因 葛罗因 生火  - 是
- Oin, Gloin. Get a fire going.  - Aye.

801
00:58:34,871 --> 00:58:35,918
好的
Right you are.

802
00:58:36,081 --> 00:58:39,711
我觉得还是继续前进比较明智
I think it would be wiser to move on.

803
00:58:40,711 --> 00:58:43,590
我们可以前往幽谷
We could make for the Hidden Valley.

804
00:58:43,880 --> 00:58:45,757
我已经告诉你了...
I have told you already...

805
00:58:45,924 --> 00:58:47,801
我不会靠近那地方
I will not go near that place.

806
00:58:47,968 --> 00:58:50,266
为什么? 精灵可以提供帮助
Why not? The Elves could help us.

807
00:58:50,429 --> 00:58:52,523
我们能补充食物 休养生息 听取建议
We could get food, rest, advice.

808
00:58:52,723 --> 00:58:54,771
我不需要精灵的建议
I do not need their advice.

809
00:58:54,975 --> 00:58:59,025
我们还有一张地图看不懂 爱隆能帮助我们
We have a map that we cannot read. Lord Elrond could help us.

810
00:58:59,187 --> 00:59:00,564
帮助?
Help?

811
00:59:01,565 --> 00:59:03,693
恶龙袭击伊鲁柏的时候
A dragon attacks Erebor.

812
00:59:03,859 --> 00:59:06,112
精灵提供帮助了吗?
What help came from the Elves?

813
00:59:07,195 --> 00:59:09,118
半兽人扫荡摩瑞亚...
Orcs plunder Moria...

814
00:59:09,281 --> 00:59:11,704
亵渎圣殿的时候
desecrate our sacred halls.

815
00:59:11,867 --> 00:59:14,746
精灵们只是袖手旁观
The Elves looked on and did nothing.

816
00:59:15,746 --> 00:59:19,796
而你却要我去找那些背叛我祖父的人
And you ask me to seek out the very people who betrayed my grandfather.

817
00:59:19,958 --> 00:59:21,255
那些背叛我父亲的人
Who betrayed my father.

818
00:59:21,418 --> 00:59:23,216
但你不是他们
You are neither of them.

819
00:59:24,087 --> 00:59:27,591
我给你地图和钥匙 不是为了让你执着于往事
I did not give you that map and key for you to hold onto the past.

820
00:59:27,758 --> 00:59:29,806
那本来就是属于我的
I did not know that they were yours to keep.

821
00:59:36,016 --> 00:59:38,735
没事吧? 甘道夫你要去哪?
Everything all right? Gandalf, where are you going?

822
00:59:38,894 --> 00:59:42,319
去找这里唯一一个有理智的人
To seek the company of the only one around here who's got any sense.

823
00:59:42,481 --> 00:59:45,155
- 是谁?  - 我自己 巴金斯先生
- And who's that?  - Myself, Mr. Baggins.

824
00:59:45,609 --> 00:59:48,112
我今天已经受够了矮人了
I've had enough of Dwarves for one day.

825
00:59:50,071 --> 00:59:51,994
快点 庞博 我们都饿了
Come on, Bombur, we're hungry.

826
00:59:52,657 --> 00:59:54,785
他会回来吗?
Is he coming back?

827
00:59:59,247 --> 01:00:00,499
他已经离开很久了
He's been a long time.

828
01:00:00,707 --> 01:00:02,004
- 谁?  - 甘道夫
- Who?  - Gandalf.

829
01:00:02,125 --> 01:00:04,298
他是个巫师 知道自己在做什么
He's a Wizard. He does as he chooses.

830
01:00:04,503 --> 01:00:07,552
拿着 帮个忙 把这个给小伙子们送去
Here, do us a favor. Take this to the lads.

831
01:00:08,131 --> 01:00:09,678
住手 你已经吃得够多了
Stop it. You've had plenty.

832
01:00:09,841 --> 01:00:13,471
饭做得不错啊 庞博 我还吃过更糟的
Aye, it's not a bad stew, Bombur. I've had worse.

833
01:00:13,637 --> 01:00:15,685
- 本来可以让朵力做的  - 哈哈哈
- Dori could've cooked it.  - Ha-ha-ha.

834
01:00:15,806 --> 01:00:18,104
太好笑了
Hilarious.

835
01:00:28,819 --> 01:00:30,116
怎么了?
What's the matter?

836
01:00:30,320 --> 01:00:34,700
- 我们本应该看着马的  - 但我们遇到了些小问题
- We're supposed to be looking after the ponies.  - Only we've encountered a slight problem.

837
01:00:34,866 --> 01:00:36,709
原本有16匹马
We had 16.

838
01:00:36,910 --> 01:00:39,709
现在只有14匹了
Now there's 14.

839
01:00:43,124 --> 01:00:45,343
黛西和伯格不见了
Daisy and Bungo are missing.

840
01:00:45,544 --> 01:00:47,342
哦 那可不妙 哈 哈
Well, that's not good. Ha, ha.

841
01:00:47,504 --> 01:00:50,132
那可糟透了 要去告诉索林吗?
And that is not good at all. Shouldn't we tell Thorin?

842
01:00:50,298 --> 01:00:53,222
呃 不要 别让他担心
Uh, no. Let's not worry him.

843
01:00:53,385 --> 01:00:56,639
身为队伍的正式飞贼 我们觉得你也许愿意去调查一下
As our official burglar, we thought you might like to look into it.

844
01:00:56,805 --> 01:00:58,182
这个 呃...
Well, uh...

845
01:00:58,723 --> 01:01:02,853
- 瞧 树像是被什么大家伙连根拔起的  - 我们也是这么想的
- Look, something big uprooted these trees.  - That was our thinking.

846
01:01:03,061 --> 01:01:07,532
应该是某种巨大且危险的东西
It's something very big and possibly quite dangerous.

847
01:01:08,400 --> 01:01:09,447
嘿
Hey.

848
01:01:10,026 --> 01:01:11,528
那里有光亮
There's a light.

849
01:01:12,195 --> 01:01:13,617
过来
Over here.

850
01:01:16,157 --> 01:01:17,158
蹲下
Stay down.

851
01:01:22,622 --> 01:01:24,044
那是什么?
What is it?

852
01:01:24,207 --> 01:01:25,629
食人妖
Trolls.

853
01:01:43,935 --> 01:01:44,936
哦
Oh.

854
01:01:52,569 --> 01:01:54,537
他又抓走了桃金娘和薄荷
He's got Myrtle and Minty.

855
01:01:55,614 --> 01:01:58,367
我想它们会被吃掉的 我们得采取行动
I think they're gonna eat them. We have to do something.

856
01:01:58,575 --> 01:02:00,373
没错 你快上吧
Yes, you should.

857
01:02:00,660 --> 01:02:04,631
食人妖脑袋又笨 动作又慢 你这么小 他们根本看不到你
Mountain Trolls are slow and stupid, and you're so small, they'll never see you.

858
01:02:04,831 --> 01:02:06,799
绝对安全 我们会跟在你身后的
It's perfectly safe. We'll be behind you.

859
01:02:06,958 --> 01:02:10,588
如果遇到麻烦 就学谷仓猫头鹰叫两声 棕色猫头鹰叫一声
If you run into trouble, hoot twice like a barn owl and once like a brown owl.

860
01:02:10,754 --> 01:02:13,724
谷仓猫头鹰叫两声 不对 棕色猫头鹰叫两... 谷仓...
Twice like a barn owl. No, twice like a brown... Once like a...

861
01:02:13,924 --> 01:02:15,847
叫... 你们确定这是个好主意吗?
Like a... Are you sure this is a good idea?

862
01:02:16,217 --> 01:02:19,266
昨天吃羊肉 今天吃羊肉...
Mutton yesterday, mutton today...

863
01:02:19,429 --> 01:02:22,899
天哪 不会明天也吃羊肉吧
and, blimey, if it don't look like mutton again tomorrow.

864
01:02:23,975 --> 01:02:25,977
别发牢骚了
Quit your griping.

865
01:02:26,186 --> 01:02:30,441
这不是羊 这是新鲜的马肉
These ain't sheep. These is fresh nags.

866
01:02:30,607 --> 01:02:35,955
哦! 我不喜欢马 从来没喜欢过 它们身上连肥肉都没有
Oh! I don't like horse. I never have. Not enough fat on them.

867
01:02:36,112 --> 01:02:38,456
总比干巴巴的老农夫好吧
Well, it's better than leathery old farmer.

868
01:02:38,615 --> 01:02:42,995
他简直是皮包骨头 到现在我牙缝里还有呢
All skin and bone, he was. I'm still picking bits of him out of me teeth.

869
01:02:44,329 --> 01:02:47,458
真棒 瞧你干的好事 鼻涕进锅里了
Well, that's lovely, that is. A floater.

870
01:02:47,666 --> 01:02:49,589
没准能添点味儿
Might improve the flavor.

871
01:02:49,751 --> 01:02:52,300
啊 这儿还有呢
Ah. There's more where that came from.

872
01:02:52,504 --> 01:02:53,801
- 哦 不 不准这样!  - 噢!
- Oh, no, you don't!  - Ow!

873
01:02:57,759 --> 01:02:59,636
坐下!
Sit down!

874
01:03:07,769 --> 01:03:11,990
希望你能把这些马的内脏去掉
Well, I hope you're gonna gut these nags.

875
01:03:12,148 --> 01:03:14,867
我不喜欢吃内脏
I don't like the stinky parts.

876
01:03:15,151 --> 01:03:17,995
- 噢!  - 我说了 坐下
- Ow!  - I said sit down.

877
01:03:18,154 --> 01:03:19,201
我饿死了!
I'm starving!

878
01:03:19,364 --> 01:03:22,459
今晚到底吃不吃马肉了?
Now, are we having horse tonight or what?

879
01:03:22,617 --> 01:03:26,667
闭上你的臭嘴 我给什么你就吃什么
Shut your cakehole. You'll eat what I give you.

880
01:03:27,539 --> 01:03:31,214
怎么让他当厨师的? 所有东西尝起来都是一个味儿
How come he's the cook? Everything tastes the same.

881
01:03:31,376 --> 01:03:33,003
所有东西吃着都像鸡肉
Everything tastes like chicken.

882
01:03:33,169 --> 01:03:34,341
除了鸡肉不像
Except the chicken.

883
01:03:34,546 --> 01:03:35,889
鸡肉倒像是鱼!
What tastes like fish!

884
01:03:36,006 --> 01:03:39,351
我刚说过 你们应该心存感激
I'm just saying, a little appreciation would be nice.

885
01:03:41,720 --> 01:03:45,475
哦 "谢谢你 伯特 做得真棒 伯特"
Oh. "Thank you very much, Bert. Lovely stew, Bert."

886
01:03:45,682 --> 01:03:49,607
- 这有什么难的?  - 嘘 嘘
- How hard is that?  - Shh. Shh, shh. Shh.

887
01:03:50,061 --> 01:03:52,860
只需要再撒些松鼠粪
Just needs a sprinkle of squirrel dung.

888
01:03:53,982 --> 01:03:55,905
嘿 那是我的酒
Here, that's my grog.

889
01:03:58,528 --> 01:04:01,532
抱歉 噢!
Sorry. Ow!

890
01:04:03,408 --> 01:04:07,663
哦 味道正好 不错
Ooh. That is beautifully balanced, that is.

891
01:04:08,288 --> 01:04:11,212
把你嘴巴凑过来接住 嗯?
Wrap your laughing gear around that, eh?

892
01:04:12,208 --> 01:04:13,209
不错吧?
Good, isn't it?

893
01:04:15,170 --> 01:04:17,719
所以要我来当厨师
That's why I'm the cook.

894
01:04:25,472 --> 01:04:29,693
哦 我肚子都叫了 我需要捞点东西吃
Oh, my guts are grumbling. I got to snaffle something.

895
01:04:29,851 --> 01:04:32,604
- 肉 我要肉  - 啊! 啊!
- Flesh, I need flesh.  - Ah! Ah!

896
01:04:36,107 --> 01:04:37,108
天哪!
Blimey!

897
01:04:37,901 --> 01:04:40,780
伯特 伯特! 看我鼻子里喷出了什么
Bert. Bert! Look what's come out of me hooter.

898
01:04:40,945 --> 01:04:43,073
它有手有脚 什么都有
It's got arms and legs and everything.

899
01:04:43,406 --> 01:04:44,874
这是什么东西?
What is it?

900
01:04:45,033 --> 01:04:47,707
我不知道 但我不喜欢它扭来扭去的样子
I don't know. But I don't like the way it wriggles around.

901
01:04:51,706 --> 01:04:54,926
你是什么东西? 特大号松鼠吗?
What are you, then? An oversized squirrel?

902
01:04:55,085 --> 01:04:56,803
我是个飞... 呃 霍比特人
I'm a burglar... Uh, Hobbit.

903
01:04:56,961 --> 01:04:59,055
一个飞蛾霍比特人?
A burglar Hobbit?

904
01:04:59,214 --> 01:05:00,841
我们能煮了他吗?
Can we cook him?

905
01:05:00,965 --> 01:05:03,559
可以试试
We can try.

906
01:05:06,346 --> 01:05:08,440
他还不够我咬一大口的
He wouldn't make more than a mouthful.

907
01:05:08,598 --> 01:05:11,397
尽管不是皮包骨头
Not when he's skinned and boned.

908
01:05:11,601 --> 01:05:14,571
也许附近还有更多的飞蛾霍比特人
Perhaps there's more burglar Hobbits around these parts.

909
01:05:14,729 --> 01:05:17,733
说不定够做个派
Might be enough for a pie.

910
01:05:18,024 --> 01:05:19,992
- 抓住他!  - 他动作太快了
- Grab him!  - He's too quick.

911
01:05:20,193 --> 01:05:23,493
好吧 快过来 你这小东...
Right. Come here, you little...

912
01:05:23,655 --> 01:05:24,872
抓住你了
Gotcha.

913
01:05:25,281 --> 01:05:28,831
你还有其他小同伴躲在不该躲的地方吗?
Are there any more of you little fellas hiding where you shouldn't?

914
01:05:29,035 --> 01:05:30,628
没有
No.

915
01:05:30,912 --> 01:05:32,164
他在撒谎
He's lying.

916
01:05:32,372 --> 01:05:36,718
- 不 我没有!  - 把他悬到火上烤
- No, I'm not!  - Hold his toes over the fire.

917
01:05:36,918 --> 01:05:39,592
让他尖叫!
Make him squeal!

918
01:05:43,007 --> 01:05:44,099
把他放下!
Drop him!

919
01:05:44,259 --> 01:05:45,681
你说什么?
You what?

920
01:05:46,469 --> 01:05:47,937
我说...
I said...

921
01:05:48,221 --> 01:05:49,268
把他放下
drop him.

922
01:06:12,203 --> 01:06:15,958
拿袋子来! 把他们用麻袋套上!
Get the sacks! Stick them in the sacks!

923
01:06:38,188 --> 01:06:39,656
噢!
Ow!

924
01:07:05,256 --> 01:07:07,429
快点! 起来!
Come on! Get up!

925
01:07:07,717 --> 01:07:09,014
- 比尔博!  - 不要!
- Bilbo!  - Don't!

926
01:07:10,637 --> 01:07:12,639
放下武器...
Lay down your arms...

927
01:07:13,306 --> 01:07:15,104
不然我们就撕了他
or we'll rip his off.

928
01:07:29,739 --> 01:07:31,741
哦! 烫死了 烫死了 烫死了!
Oh! That's hot, that's hot, that's hot!

929
01:07:31,908 --> 01:07:33,535
别费劲煮他们了
Don't bother cooking them.

930
01:07:33,701 --> 01:07:37,956
我们直接坐上去 把他们压成肉酱吧
Let's just sit on them and squash them into jelly.

931
01:07:38,122 --> 01:07:42,298
应该先这样爆炒再煎烤 最后撒些鼠尾草
They should be sauteed and grilled with a sprinkle of sage.

932
01:07:42,502 --> 01:07:44,004
这真的有必要吗?
Is this really necessary?

933
01:07:44,212 --> 01:07:45,964
听起来确实不错
That does sound quite nice.

934
01:07:46,130 --> 01:07:48,599
- 松开我 先生  - 去吃和你个子一样大的东西吧
- Untie me, mister.  - Eat someone your own size.

935
01:07:49,300 --> 01:07:51,223
别介意调料了
Never mind the seasoning.

936
01:07:51,386 --> 01:07:53,138
我们没有一整晚的时间
We ain't got all night.

937
01:07:53,346 --> 01:07:56,691
黎明不远了 我们动作快点
Dawn ain't far away. Let's get a move on.

938
01:07:56,808 --> 01:07:59,277
我可不想被变成石头
I don't fancy being turned to stone.

939
01:08:01,980 --> 01:08:03,323
等等!
Wait!

940
01:08:03,481 --> 01:08:06,485
你们犯了个大错
You are making a terrible mistake.

941
01:08:06,651 --> 01:08:08,904
你没法和他们讲道理 他们是白痴!
You can't reason with them. They're half-wits!

942
01:08:09,070 --> 01:08:11,164
白痴? 那我们成什么了?
Half-wits? What does that make us?

943
01:08:11,781 --> 01:08:14,580
我指的是调料的事
I meant with the seasoning.

944
01:08:14,909 --> 01:08:17,503
调料怎么了?
What about the seasoning?

945
01:08:17,704 --> 01:08:18,956
你闻过他们的味道了么?
Well, have you smelt them?

946
01:08:19,289 --> 01:08:22,839
想把他们烤熟装盘 你就得用比鼠尾草味道更重的调料
You're gonna need something stronger than sage before you plate this lot up.

947
01:08:23,001 --> 01:08:26,096
- 叛徒!  - 你懂怎么煮矮人?
- Traitor!  - What do you know about cooking Dwarf?

948
01:08:26,671 --> 01:08:27,718
闭嘴
Shut up.

949
01:08:28,047 --> 01:08:31,722
让 小格灰灰霍比特人来说
Let the flurgaburburhobbit talk.

950
01:08:32,635 --> 01:08:35,559
煮矮人的秘诀就在于...
The secret to cooking Dwarf is...

951
01:08:35,722 --> 01:08:38,817
- 嗯? 说吧 告诉我们秘诀  - 呃 就是...
- Yes? Come on. Tell us the secret.  - It's, uh...

952
01:08:39,017 --> 01:08:41,065
我正准备说呢 秘诀就是...
Yes, I'm telling you. The secret is...

953
01:08:43,604 --> 01:08:45,356
先剥皮
to skin them first.

954
01:08:45,523 --> 01:08:47,491
什么? 剥我们的皮?
What? Skin us?

955
01:08:47,608 --> 01:08:50,157
汤姆 给我拿切片刀来
Tom, get me filleting knife.

956
01:08:50,320 --> 01:08:51,993
我要剥了你的皮! 你这小...
I'll skin you, you little...!

957
01:08:52,155 --> 01:08:54,032
我不会忘记这件事的 我绝不会忘记
I won't forget that. I won't forget it.

958
01:08:54,198 --> 01:08:56,496
都是废话
What a load of rubbish.

959
01:08:56,701 --> 01:08:59,625
我吃过好多带皮的
I've eaten plenty with their skins on.

960
01:08:59,787 --> 01:09:02,165
一口吞下 连靴子也吃下去
Scarf them, I say, boots and all.

961
01:09:02,790 --> 01:09:05,088
他说的对
He's right.

962
01:09:05,209 --> 01:09:07,883
吃些活矮人也没关系
Nothing wrong with a bit of raw Dwarf.

963
01:09:10,631 --> 01:09:12,804
美味又松脆
Nice and crunchy.

964
01:09:13,134 --> 01:09:15,683
不 别挑那个 他被感染了
Oh, not that one. He's infected.

965
01:09:15,970 --> 01:09:17,597
- 嗯?  - 你说什么?
- Huh?  - You what?

966
01:09:17,764 --> 01:09:21,860
没错 他肠道里有虫子
Yeah, he's got worms in his tubes.

967
01:09:22,060 --> 01:09:24,028
- 呕!  - 啊!
- Eww!  - Aah!

968
01:09:24,270 --> 01:09:27,524
事实上 他们都被感染了 他们体内长满了寄生虫
In fact, they all have. They're infested with parasites.

969
01:09:27,690 --> 01:09:30,694
那真是太可怕了 我可不会冒这种险 绝对不会
It's a terrible business. I wouldn't risk it. I really wouldn't.

970
01:09:30,860 --> 01:09:32,737
寄生虫? 他说了 "寄生虫" ?
Parasites? Did he say "parasites"?

971
01:09:32,904 --> 01:09:35,703
我们没有寄生虫 你才有寄生虫呢!
We don't have parasites. You have parasites!

972
01:09:36,407 --> 01:09:38,375
你在说什么呢 小伙子?
What are you talking about, laddie?

973
01:09:41,913 --> 01:09:43,790
我的寄生虫和手臂一样粗
I've got parasites as big as my arm.

974
01:09:43,956 --> 01:09:46,550
我的寄生虫最大了 超大号寄生虫
Mine are the biggest parasites. I've got huge parasites.

975
01:09:48,586 --> 01:09:50,054
- 我们身上到处都是  - 没错 我全身都是
- We're riddled.  - Yes, I'm riddled.

976
01:09:50,213 --> 01:09:51,510
是的 我们糟透了
Yes, we are, badly.

977
01:09:51,672 --> 01:09:54,551
那么你要我们怎么办?
What would you have us do, then?

978
01:09:54,717 --> 01:09:56,219
放他们走?
Let them all go?

979
01:09:56,677 --> 01:09:59,931
- 这个...  - 你以为我不知道你想干什么?
- Well...  - You think I don't know what you're up to?

980
01:10:00,390 --> 01:10:04,486
这只小耗子把我们当傻子耍呢
This little ferret is taking us for fools.

981
01:10:04,936 --> 01:10:06,483
- 耗子?  - 傻子?
- Ferret?  - Fools?

982
01:10:06,646 --> 01:10:09,570
曙光将把你们全部消灭
The dawn will take you all.

983
01:10:11,025 --> 01:10:12,618
- 那是谁?  - 不知道
- Who's that?  - No idea.

984
01:10:12,777 --> 01:10:13,949
我们能把他也吃了吗?
Can we eat him too?

985
01:10:40,096 --> 01:10:42,645
把你的脚从我背上拿开
Get your foot out of my back.

986
01:10:48,604 --> 01:10:49,901
啊
Ah.

987
01:10:52,150 --> 01:10:54,323
容我问一句 你之前去哪里了?
Where did you go to, if I may ask?

988
01:10:54,444 --> 01:10:56,162
去前面看看
To look ahead.

989
01:10:56,487 --> 01:10:59,331
- 你为什么又回来了?  - 看看后面
- What brought you back?  - Looking behind.

990
01:11:00,324 --> 01:11:01,576
真糟糕
Nasty business.

991
01:11:01,742 --> 01:11:03,244
幸好 大家都没事
Still, they're all in one piece.

992
01:11:03,411 --> 01:11:04,913
你的飞贼可没什么功劳
No thanks to your burglar.

993
01:11:06,330 --> 01:11:08,458
他给你们争取了时间
He had the nous to play for time.

994
01:11:09,876 --> 01:11:12,254
你们都没有意识到这点
None of the rest of you thought of that.

995
01:11:14,338 --> 01:11:17,262
这些食人妖一定都是从伊顿荒原来的
They must have come down from the Ettenmoors.

996
01:11:17,425 --> 01:11:20,178
从什么时候开始 他们会往南走得这么远?
Since when do Mountain Trolls venture this far south?

997
01:11:20,386 --> 01:11:22,480
哦 没多久
Ooh. Not for an age.

998
01:11:23,264 --> 01:11:26,643
就在黑暗势力统治这片土地之后
Not since a darker power ruled these lands.

999
01:11:32,523 --> 01:11:36,118
他们不能在白天活动
They could not have moved in daylight.

1000
01:11:36,652 --> 01:11:39,030
这附近一定会有个洞穴
There must be a cave nearby.

1001
01:11:49,665 --> 01:11:51,963
哦 这股臭味是哪来的?
Oh, what's that stench?

1002
01:11:52,126 --> 01:11:55,300
这里是食人妖的巢穴
It's a Troll-hoard.

1003
01:11:55,671 --> 01:11:58,220
小心你们摸到的东西
Be careful what you touch.

1004
01:12:10,686 --> 01:12:13,781
把财宝随意扔放 好像太可惜了
Seems a shame just to leave it lying around.

1005
01:12:15,191 --> 01:12:17,819
- 谁都可以拿走  - 同意
- Anyone could take it.  - Agreed.

1006
01:12:17,985 --> 01:12:19,658
- 诺力  - 干什么?
- Nori.  - Yeah?

1007
01:12:19,820 --> 01:12:21,197
拿把铲子来
Get a shovel.

1008
01:12:38,464 --> 01:12:40,512
这些剑不是食人妖做的
These swords were not made by any Troll.

1009
01:12:46,514 --> 01:12:50,735
也不是人类铁匠做的
Nor were they made by any smith among men.

1010
01:12:55,481 --> 01:12:57,529
这些是第一纪的高等精灵...
These were forged in Gondolin...

1011
01:12:57,692 --> 01:13:01,196
在贡多林锻造的
by the High Elves of the First Age.

1012
01:13:01,696 --> 01:13:03,915
没有比这更锋利的刀刃了
You could not wish for a finer blade.

1013
01:13:17,920 --> 01:13:19,718
- 把它埋起来  - 太好了
- Set it down.  - That's good.

1014
01:13:20,673 --> 01:13:22,346
好了 继续 快点
All right, come on. Quick.

1015
01:13:30,683 --> 01:13:33,357
我们也存点长期储蓄
We're making a long-term deposit.

1016
01:13:33,978 --> 01:13:35,579
我们快离开这个臭烘烘的地方吧
Let's get out of this foul place.

1017
01:13:36,022 --> 01:13:37,649
走吧 我们走
Come on, let's go.

1018
01:13:37,857 --> 01:13:39,825
跟上 波佛 葛罗因 诺力
Bofur, Gloin, Nori.

1019
01:13:59,295 --> 01:14:01,013
- 比尔博  - 嗯?
- Bilbo.  - Hmm?

1020
01:14:02,506 --> 01:14:03,507
给你
Here.

1021
01:14:03,716 --> 01:14:06,265
这个尺寸正适合你
This is about your size.

1022
01:14:11,932 --> 01:14:13,309
我不能接受它
I can't take this.

1023
01:14:13,684 --> 01:14:15,652
这把剑是精灵制作的...
The blade is of Elvish make...

1024
01:14:15,853 --> 01:14:20,825
也就是说当半兽人或哥布林靠近的时候 它会发出蓝色的光
which means it will glow blue when Orcs or Goblins are nearby.

1025
01:14:21,984 --> 01:14:24,328
我这辈子都没用过剑
I have never used a sword in my life.

1026
01:14:24,487 --> 01:14:26,455
我希望你永远用不上它
And I hope you never have to.

1027
01:14:27,406 --> 01:14:29,079
但是如果你用到了 要记住
But if you do, remember this:

1028
01:14:30,493 --> 01:14:35,795
真正的勇气 不是体现在杀戮的时候...
True courage is about knowing not when to take a life...

1029
01:14:36,457 --> 01:14:38,676
而是宽恕的时候
but when to spare one.

1030
01:14:44,006 --> 01:14:45,553
有什么东西过来了!
Something's coming!

1031
01:14:45,716 --> 01:14:47,844
- 甘道夫  - 聚在一起!
- Gandalf.  - Stay together!

1032
01:14:48,678 --> 01:14:52,057
快点! 拿上武器!
Hurry now! Arm yourselves!

1033
01:15:09,865 --> 01:15:13,244
小偷! 大火! 谋杀!
Thieves! Fire! Murder!

1034
01:15:14,551 --> 01:15:16,427
瑞达加斯特
Radagast.

1035
01:15:16,929 --> 01:15:18,804
这是褐袍瑞达加斯特
It's Radagast the Brown.

1036
01:15:19,056 --> 01:15:20,681
那么...
Well...

1037
01:15:22,935 --> 01:15:24,560
你来这里到底要干什么?
What on earth are you doing here?

1038
01:15:24,811 --> 01:15:26,270
我在找你 甘道夫
I was looking for you, Gandalf.

1039
01:15:26,522 --> 01:15:27,813
出事了
Something's wrong.

1040
01:15:28,065 --> 01:15:29,357
出大事了
Something's terribly wrong.

1041
01:15:30,359 --> 01:15:31,526
怎么了?
Yes?

1042
01:15:34,029 --> 01:15:35,279
哦
Oh.

1043
01:15:36,949 --> 01:15:38,866
稍等一下
Just give me a minute.

1044
01:15:39,117 --> 01:15:42,036
哦 我有件事想说 但是我给忘了
Oh. I had a thought and now I've lost it.

1045
01:15:42,287 --> 01:15:43,788
它就在...
It was right there...

1046
01:15:44,039 --> 01:15:45,665
我的舌尖上
on the tip of my tongue.

1047
01:15:46,250 --> 01:15:46,916
哦
Oh.

1048
01:15:47,209 --> 01:15:49,377
它根本不是一件事
It's not a thought at all.

1049
01:15:49,628 --> 01:15:50,753
它是一只笨笨的...
It's a silly old...

1050
01:15:52,422 --> 01:15:54,257
老竹节虫
stick insect.

1051
01:15:58,303 --> 01:16:02,056
巨绿森林生病了 甘道夫
The Greenwood is sick, Gandalf.

1052
01:16:02,558 --> 01:16:04,684
黑暗已经将它笼罩
A darkness has fallen over it.

1053
01:16:04,935 --> 01:16:06,936
万物都不再生长
Nothing grows anymore.

1054
01:16:07,312 --> 01:16:09,313
至少 美好的东西都不再生长
At least, nothing good.

1055
01:16:09,565 --> 01:16:12,149
空气中弥漫着浑浊的腐臭
The air is foul with decay.

1056
01:16:12,401 --> 01:16:14,110
更糟糕的是蛛网
But worse are the webs.

1057
01:16:14,361 --> 01:16:16,445
蛛网? 什么意思?
Webs? What do you mean?

1058
01:16:16,697 --> 01:16:18,739
蜘蛛 甘道夫
Spiders, Gandalf.

1059
01:16:18,991 --> 01:16:20,324
巨型的蜘蛛
Giant ones.

1060
01:16:20,576 --> 01:16:24,870
我肯定是昂哥立安的后代 否则我就不是个巫师
Some kind of spawn of Ungoliant, or I am not a Wizard.

1061
01:16:25,247 --> 01:16:27,248
我沿着它们的踪迹
I followed their trail.

1062
01:16:27,499 --> 01:16:30,293
追踪到它们来自多尔戈多
They came from Dol Guldur.

1063
01:16:31,378 --> 01:16:32,920
啊?
Huh?

1064
01:16:33,213 --> 01:16:35,172
来自多尔戈多?
Dol Guldur?

1065
01:16:35,424 --> 01:16:38,593
但是那座古老的堡垒已经被废弃了
But the old fortress is abandoned.

1066
01:16:39,469 --> 01:16:41,220
不 甘道夫
No, Gandalf.

1067
01:16:42,639 --> 01:16:44,557
那里有人
It's not.

1068
01:16:52,816 --> 01:16:55,568
一股黑暗势力盘踞在那里...
A dark power dwells in there...

1069
01:16:55,819 --> 01:16:57,695
那是我从未感受过的...
Such as I have never...

1070
01:16:57,946 --> 01:16:59,488
黑暗
felt before.

1071
01:17:00,991 --> 01:17:05,328
那是远古魔影
It is The Shadow of an ancient horror.

1072
01:17:11,418 --> 01:17:14,754
它可以召唤...
One that can summon the spirits...

1073
01:17:15,255 --> 01:17:15,921
亡者之灵
of the dead.

1074
01:17:33,482 --> 01:17:34,940
我看到他了 甘道夫
I saw him, Gandalf.

1075
01:17:36,109 --> 01:17:38,736
从黑暗中...
From out of the darkness...

1076
01:17:39,154 --> 01:17:40,029
走出来的是...
a Necromancer...

1077
01:17:41,365 --> 01:17:42,281
一位
has come.

1078
01:17:43,158 --> 01:17:45,409
死灵法师
Radagast.

1079
01:17:50,832 --> 01:17:52,583
快! 快! 快点! 快点!
Quick! Quick, quick! Quick, quick!

1080
01:17:55,420 --> 01:17:56,420
等等我!
Wait for me!

1081
01:18:10,811 --> 01:18:11,977
对不起
Sorry.

1082
01:18:12,229 --> 01:18:14,563
来一口老托比吧
Try a little Old Toby.

1083
01:18:14,815 --> 01:18:16,315
它能帮你放松下来
It'll help settle your nerves.

1084
01:18:19,903 --> 01:18:20,945
吐出来
And out.

1085
01:18:28,704 --> 01:18:29,495
现在好好想想...
Now...

1086
01:18:29,746 --> 01:18:33,207
你确定那是死灵法师吗?
a Necromancer. Are you sure?

1087
01:18:46,805 --> 01:18:48,264
那可不是...
That is not...

1088
01:18:48,515 --> 01:18:52,560
来自我们这个世界的东西
from the world of the living.

1089
01:18:58,483 --> 01:19:01,235
那是狼吗? 这附近有狼吗?
Was that a wolf? Are there wolves out there?

1090
01:19:01,486 --> 01:19:04,280
狼? 不 那不是一般的狼
Wolves? No, that is not a wolf.

1091
01:19:09,828 --> 01:19:11,328
奇力! 射箭!
Kili! Get your bow!

1092
01:19:18,587 --> 01:19:20,004
前锋座狼
Warg scouts.

1093
01:19:20,255 --> 01:19:22,214
这说明半兽人的队伍已经不远了
Which means an Orc pack is not far behind.

1094
01:19:22,466 --> 01:19:23,340
半兽人的队伍?
Orc pack?

1095
01:19:23,592 --> 01:19:24,925
除了你的族人之外...
Who did you tell about your quest...

1096
01:19:25,177 --> 01:19:26,343
你还把这次探险的事告诉谁了?
beyond your kin?

1097
01:19:26,845 --> 01:19:27,511
谁都没有
No one.

1098
01:19:27,763 --> 01:19:28,429
你到底告诉谁了?
Who did you tell?

1099
01:19:28,680 --> 01:19:29,889
没有 我发誓
No one, I swear.

1100
01:19:30,474 --> 01:19:31,140
以杜林之名...
What in...

1101
01:19:31,391 --> 01:19:32,391
告诉我出了什么麻烦?
Durin's name is going on?

1102
01:19:32,642 --> 01:19:33,768
你们掉进陷阱了
You are being hunted.

1103
01:19:35,479 --> 01:19:36,687
我们得离开这里
We have to get out of here.

1104
01:19:36,938 --> 01:19:38,063
我们没法离开 我们没有小马了
We can't. We have no ponies.

1105
01:19:39,316 --> 01:19:40,900
它们跑散了
They bolted.

1106
01:19:41,151 --> 01:19:42,401
我去引开他们
I'll draw them off.

1107
01:19:42,652 --> 01:19:44,361
他们是刚达巴的座狼
These are Gundabad Wargs.

1108
01:19:44,613 --> 01:19:45,529
你跑不过他们的
They will outrun you.

1109
01:19:45,781 --> 01:19:47,615
这些是罗斯加堡的兔子
These are Rhosgobel rabbits.

1110
01:19:48,784 --> 01:19:52,036
我倒想让它们比试比试
I'd like to see them try.

1111
01:20:00,712 --> 01:20:02,880
来啊! 来啊!
Come on! Come on!

1112
01:20:03,131 --> 01:20:05,382
来抓我啊! 哈哈!
Come and get me! Ha, ha!

1113
01:20:14,684 --> 01:20:16,310
过来
Come on.

1114
01:20:44,214 --> 01:20:45,256
别走散了
Stay together.

1115
01:20:45,507 --> 01:20:46,507
快跑!
Move!

1116
01:20:57,769 --> 01:21:00,229
欧力 停! 回来
Ori, no! Get back.

1117
01:21:03,400 --> 01:21:04,733
所有人 过来 快!
All of you, come on. Quick!

1118
01:21:07,988 --> 01:21:09,905
你要带我们去哪?
Where are you leading us?

1119
01:22:18,475 --> 01:22:19,516
快跑!
Move!

1120
01:22:19,768 --> 01:22:20,935
快!
Run!

1121
01:22:37,911 --> 01:22:39,453
他们在那里!
There they are!

1122
01:22:41,081 --> 01:22:42,081
这边走!
This way!

1123
01:22:42,332 --> 01:22:43,374
快点!
Quickly!

1124
01:22:54,761 --> 01:22:56,178
来的越来越多了!
There's more coming!

1125
01:22:57,180 --> 01:22:57,846
奇力!
Kili!

1126
01:22:58,348 --> 01:22:59,807
射箭!
Shoot them!

1127
01:23:04,229 --> 01:23:05,813
我们被包围了!
We're surrounded!

1128
01:23:10,151 --> 01:23:11,568
甘道夫在哪里?
Where's Gandalf?

1129
01:23:11,820 --> 01:23:13,946
他抛弃了我们
He's abandoned us.

1130
01:23:19,995 --> 01:23:22,287
稳住阵脚!
Hold your ground!

1131
01:23:31,715 --> 01:23:32,881
来这边 你们这些傻瓜!
This way, you fools!

1132
01:23:33,883 --> 01:23:35,050
过来 快!
Come on, move!

1133
01:23:37,387 --> 01:23:38,095
快点!
Quickly!

1134
01:23:38,346 --> 01:23:39,263
大家都来这里!
All of you!

1135
01:23:39,514 --> 01:23:40,889
过来!
Come on!

1136
01:23:41,683 --> 01:23:42,766
快 快 快!
Go, go, go!

1137
01:23:53,445 --> 01:23:54,319
八 九 十
Eight, nine, ten.

1138
01:23:56,698 --> 01:23:57,406
快点! 奇力!
Kili!

1139
01:23:57,657 --> 01:23:58,657
快过来!
Run!

1140
01:24:38,823 --> 01:24:40,157
是精灵
Elves.

1141
01:24:43,036 --> 01:24:44,036
我看不出来...
I cannot see...

1142
01:24:44,287 --> 01:24:46,914
这条路通向哪里 我们走不走?
where the pathway leads. Do we follow it or no?

1143
01:24:47,165 --> 01:24:49,083
当然要走
Follow it, of course.

1144
01:24:52,253 --> 01:24:54,421
明智的选择
I think that would be wise.

1145
01:25:17,570 --> 01:25:18,487
甘道夫
Gandalf.

1146
01:25:19,072 --> 01:25:20,531
我们这是在哪?
Where are we?

1147
01:25:20,782 --> 01:25:21,657
你有感觉?
You can feel it?

1148
01:25:21,908 --> 01:25:25,536
是啊 感觉就像是...
Yes. It feels like...

1149
01:25:26,287 --> 01:25:27,496
像是有魔法一样
Well, like magic.

1150
01:25:27,747 --> 01:25:30,207
那就对了
That's exactly what it is.

1151
01:25:30,458 --> 01:25:33,293
这是非常强大的魔法
A very powerful magic.

1152
01:25:34,170 --> 01:25:36,380
前面有光
There's light ahead.

1153
01:26:16,880 --> 01:26:19,631
这是伊姆拉崔河谷
The Valley of Imladris.

1154
01:26:20,884 --> 01:26:24,219
更多的时候 它有另一个名字
In the common tongue, it's known by another name.

1155
01:26:25,096 --> 01:26:26,555
瑞文戴尔
Rivendell.

1156
01:26:29,392 --> 01:26:34,313
这里是大海东岸最后的美丽家园
Here lies the Last Homely House East of the Sea.

1157
01:26:35,315 --> 01:26:36,648
这都是你计划好的
This was your plan all along.

1158
01:26:38,651 --> 01:26:40,652
向我们的敌人寻求帮助
To seek refuge with our enemy.

1159
01:26:40,904 --> 01:26:44,156
这里没有你的敌人 索林・橡木盾
You have no enemies here, Thorin Oakenshield.

1160
01:26:44,407 --> 01:26:46,283
如果你在林谷里...
The only ill will to be found...

1161
01:26:46,534 --> 01:26:48,327
感到任何敌意 那也是你自己身上的
in this valley is that which you bring yourself.

1162
01:26:49,621 --> 01:26:52,789
你以为精灵会为我们的探险祝福吗?
You think the Elves will give our quest their blessing?

1163
01:26:53,958 --> 01:26:55,334
他们会阻止我们
They will try to stop us.

1164
01:26:55,585 --> 01:26:59,546
没错 但是我们也有疑问需要他们指点
Of course they will. But we have questions that need to be answered.

1165
01:27:03,092 --> 01:27:06,637
所以如果我们想成功 和精灵的接触就需要机智
If we are to be successful, this will need to be handled with tact.

1166
01:27:06,888 --> 01:27:08,180
和尊重
And respect.

1167
01:27:08,431 --> 01:27:10,849
以及一定的风度
And no small degree of charm.

1168
01:27:11,100 --> 01:27:15,103
所以待会儿的谈判 就交给我吧
Which is why you will leave the talking to me.

1169
01:28:11,577 --> 01:28:12,411
米斯兰迪尔
Mithrandir.

1170
01:28:14,122 --> 01:28:14,913
啊
Ah.

1171
01:28:15,164 --> 01:28:16,581
林迪尔
Lindir.

1172
01:28:16,833 --> 01:28:18,375
注意点
Stay sharp.

1173
01:28:19,233 --> 01:28:20,775
我们听说你来到了幽谷

1174
01:28:21,879 --> 01:28:23,672
我有事得和爱隆谈谈
I must speak with Lord Elrond.

1175
01:28:23,965 --> 01:28:25,882
爱隆殿下不在这里
My Lord Elrond is not here.

1176
01:28:26,384 --> 01:28:28,093
不在这里?
Not here?

1177
01:28:29,053 --> 01:28:30,095
他在哪?
Where is he?

1178
01:28:44,944 --> 01:28:46,570
靠紧!
Close ranks!

1179
01:29:10,595 --> 01:29:11,636
甘道夫
Gandalf.

1180
01:29:11,888 --> 01:29:13,930
爱隆
Lord Elrond.

1181
01:29:14,888 --> 01:29:16,930
我的朋友

1182
01:29:17,388 --> 01:29:18,630
你去哪了?

1183
01:29:18,988 --> 01:29:22,130
我们出去击退了一群南边来的半兽人

1184
01:29:24,988 --> 01:29:27,630
我们在密道附近杀死了几个

1185
01:29:30,740 --> 01:29:34,743
这很奇怪 半兽人离我们的边界这么近
Strange for Orcs to come so close to our borders.

1186
01:29:34,994 --> 01:29:38,914
是什么人或者什么事引他们过来的
Something or someone has drawn them near.

1187
01:29:39,165 --> 01:29:41,458
啊 那大概是我们
Ah. That may have been us.

1188
01:29:46,464 --> 01:29:49,758
欢迎你 索恩之子索林
Welcome, Thorin, son of Thrain.

1189
01:29:50,009 --> 01:29:52,386
我想我们没见过
I do not believe we have met.

1190
01:29:52,887 --> 01:29:55,889
你有你祖父的风范
You have your grandfather's bearing.

1191
01:29:56,140 --> 01:29:57,641
索尔统治山脉的时候...
I knew Thror when he ruled...

1192
01:29:57,892 --> 01:30:02,062
- 我认识他  - 真的? 他从没提起过你
- Under the Mountain.  - Indeed? He made no mention of you.

1193
01:30:05,292 --> 01:30:08,862
生起炉火 盛上美酒 我们得款待我们的客人(辛达语)
Nartho i noer, toltho i viruvor. Boe i annam vann a nethail vin.

1194
01:30:13,282 --> 01:30:15,492
他在说什么?
What is he saying?

1195
01:30:15,743 --> 01:30:18,120
他是在侮辱我们吗?
Does he offer us insult?

1196
01:30:18,371 --> 01:30:21,998
不 葛罗因 他要为你们提供食物
No, Master Gloin, he's offering you food.

1197
01:30:28,673 --> 01:30:29,714
好吧...
Well...

1198
01:30:29,966 --> 01:30:31,883
这样的话 带路吧
in that case, lead on.

1199
01:30:33,219 --> 01:30:34,261
嘿 来吧
Hey. Come on.

1200
01:30:34,595 --> 01:30:37,389
试试嘛 就吃一口
Try it. Just a mouthful.

1201
01:30:37,640 --> 01:30:39,182
我不喜欢绿叶菜
I don't like green food.

1202
01:30:40,435 --> 01:30:41,351
肉在哪里?
Where's the meat?

1203
01:30:43,062 --> 01:30:44,521
他们这里有薯片吗?
Have they got any chips?

1204
01:30:45,523 --> 01:30:46,314
感谢你...
Kind of you...

1205
01:30:46,566 --> 01:30:47,941
招待我们
to invite us.

1206
01:30:48,192 --> 01:30:49,693
我都没穿正式的服装
Not really dressed for dinner.

1207
01:30:49,944 --> 01:30:51,111
你从来都没穿过
Well, you never are.

1208
01:31:10,756 --> 01:31:13,758
我个人感觉不是太喜欢女精灵 她们太瘦了
I can't say I fancy Elf maids myself, too thin.

1209
01:31:14,218 --> 01:31:15,760
她们都有高高的颧骨...
They're all high cheekbones...

1210
01:31:16,012 --> 01:31:18,013
和雪白的皮肤
and creamy skin.

1211
01:31:18,306 --> 01:31:19,639
我觉得她们的头发也不够浓密
Not enough facial hair for me.

1212
01:31:19,891 --> 01:31:23,518
不过那边的那个还不错
Although that one there is not bad.

1213
01:31:24,854 --> 01:31:26,313
那不是个女精灵
That's not an Elf maid.

1214
01:31:38,367 --> 01:31:40,035
有点意思
That's funny.

1215
01:31:51,422 --> 01:31:55,467
这是奥格瑞斯特 哥布林斩杀者
This is Orcrist, the Goblin-cleaver.

1216
01:31:55,718 --> 01:31:57,260
是由我的同族...
A famous blade...

1217
01:31:57,512 --> 01:32:02,849
西方高等精灵锻造的著名的宝剑
forged by the High Elves of the West, my kin.

1218
01:32:03,559 --> 01:32:05,393
愿它能够帮助你
May it serve you well.

1219
01:32:05,645 --> 01:32:06,436
这是...
And this...

1220
01:32:06,687 --> 01:32:08,021
格兰瑞...
is Glamdring...

1221
01:32:09,690 --> 01:32:11,149
敌击剑 这是...
the Foehammer. Sword...

1222
01:32:11,400 --> 01:32:13,485
贡多林之王的宝剑
of the King of Gondolin.

1223
01:32:13,736 --> 01:32:16,196
这些是为第一纪元的哥布林大战铸造的
These were made for the Goblin Wars of the First Age.

1224
01:32:16,447 --> 01:32:17,489
我没有冒犯的意思 年轻人
I wouldn't bother, laddie.

1225
01:32:17,740 --> 01:32:21,159
宝剑是以它在战争中的功勋命名的
Swords are named for the great deeds they do in war.

1226
01:32:21,410 --> 01:32:23,662
你什么意思 我的剑没有经历过战争?
What are you saying, my sword hasn't seen battle?

1227
01:32:24,163 --> 01:32:26,164
我都不确定它是一把剑
I'm not actually sure it is a sword.

1228
01:32:28,084 --> 01:32:29,584
它更像是一把拆信刀 真的
More of a letter opener, really.

1229
01:32:31,212 --> 01:32:32,629
- 你是怎么得到这些的?  - 我们是在...
- How did you come by these?  - We found them...

1230
01:32:32,880 --> 01:32:35,131
东方大道上的一个食人妖巢穴找到的...
in a Troll-hoard on the Great East Road...

1231
01:32:35,716 --> 01:32:36,633
就在...
shortly before...

1232
01:32:36,884 --> 01:32:40,887
- 我们被半兽人攻击之前  - 你们在...
- we were ambushed by Orcs.  - And what were you doing...

1233
01:32:41,138 --> 01:32:43,306
东方大道上干什么?
on the Great East Road?

1234
01:32:44,475 --> 01:32:45,684
不好意思
Excuse me.

1235
01:32:53,317 --> 01:32:54,901
十三个矮人...
Thirteen Dwarves...

1236
01:32:55,152 --> 01:32:56,570
和一个半身人
and a Halfling. Hm.

1237
01:32:56,821 --> 01:32:59,781
真是奇怪的旅行伙伴啊 甘道夫
Strange traveling companions, Gandalf.

1238
01:33:00,032 --> 01:33:02,534
他们都是杜林矮人的后代
These are the descendants of the house of Durin.

1239
01:33:02,785 --> 01:33:04,744
他们出身贵族 行事得体
They're noble, decent folk.

1240
01:33:04,996 --> 01:33:07,622
而且都非常有教养
And they're surprisingly cultured.

1241
01:33:08,124 --> 01:33:08,873
他们都非常...
They've got a deep love...

1242
01:33:09,125 --> 01:33:11,668
- 热爱艺术  - 换首曲子 行不行?
- of the arts.  - Change the tune, why don't you?

1243
01:33:11,919 --> 01:33:13,503
我感觉像是在参加葬礼
I feel like I'm at a funeral.

1244
01:33:13,754 --> 01:33:15,130
- 有人死了吗?  - 好吧...
- Did somebody die?  - All right...

1245
01:33:15,381 --> 01:33:17,716
伙计们 看我的
lads. There's only one thing for it.

1246
